Quote:  This red tussock, or snow grass, grows abundantly in the Mataura district, and would be used very extensively but for the fact that it is very stubborn to work, requiring a long treatment in the digester and a strong solution of soda, which reduces its bulk very much, making it more profitable to use made material, of which a good supply is now procurable.
